                  <msItem n="1" class="fas">
                     <locus from="1r:1" to="11v:11"/>
                     <title ref="#hsg" type="uniform">Hrómundar saga Gripssonar</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="non"/>
                     <rubric>Saga af Hromunde Greipssyne</rubric>
                     <incipit>Sa k<ex>onung</ex>r reþe f<ex>yrir</ex> Gorþom i Danm<ex>or</ex>k e<ex>r</ex> Olafr het</incipit>
                     <finalRubric>oc lykr hier saugo Hromundz Greipssonar.</finalRubric>
                     <colophon>Su saga sem þetta var effter skriffad vard naumlega lesen<ex>n</ex> og ei sem skilian legust
                     um landa edur stada heite sum. Þö er þad vyst ad räda hier af kong Olafur mune verid hafa kongur ad nafnbök i Norex velldj
                     einhuórs stadar. þar sem nær grendsad hefur vid Svyþiöd, þvy þä hefur Norex ryke haft marga smäa k<ex>onun</ex>ga
                     sem breysast kan<ex>n</ex> af fornum frædum. so skrifar Sr. <name type="person" key="MagOla002">Magnus i Laufäse Olafs<ex>syne</ex>
                        </name> etc.</colophon>
                     
                     <note>Colophon appears to be in a slightly later hand.</note>
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
